  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮✨ <strong>Step into the enchanting world of T.I.MO!</strong> ✨🎮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌎 <strong>See the world through the eyes of a child!</strong> <strong>Triaventuras</strong> is a whimsical 2D point-and-click puzzle adventure where YOU take control of three unique characters—Mao, Pao, and Clau. Each one magically sees the world, and it’s up to you to use their perspectives to solve puzzles, outsmart riddles, and help adorable monsters find their way home. 🏡🐾</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/3f0619434f3b9dbae2432f880c4975d6.avif?t=1733497646\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras_big/3f0619434f3b9dbae2432f880c4975d6.avif?t=1733497646 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🔍 <strong>Core mechanic:</strong> The solution is always right before you, but the right point of view makes all the difference! Shift between perspectives to unlock secrets, explore colorful worlds and unleash your inner problem solver. 🧩💡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/027da1cb3827c46123efda17d2578b52.poster.avif?t=1733497646\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/027da1cb3827c46123efda17d2578b52.webm?t=1733497646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/027da1cb3827c46123efda17d2578b52.mp4?t=1733497646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧙‍♂️ Along the way, meet the legendary <strong>Mohan</strong>—a mythological spirit who’s lost his magic and his way. Mao, Pao, and Clau must recover his magical items to restore his powers and return him to the river he calls home. 🌊✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/48ea323989753fbd3b341fc4a8cd10e7.poster.avif?t=1733497646\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/48ea323989753fbd3b341fc4a8cd10e7.webm?t=1733497646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/48ea323989753fbd3b341fc4a8cd10e7.mp4?t=1733497646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 <strong>What are you waiting for?</strong> Dive into this heartfelt, brain-bending adventure and discover the world like never before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/8b4b9da1f89c919eac769ada34bc0b05.poster.avif?t=1733497646\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/8b4b9da1f89c919eac769ada34bc0b05.webm?t=1733497646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/8b4b9da1f89c919eac769ada34bc0b05.mp4?t=1733497646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹️ <strong>Download T.I.M.O now and let the Triaventuras begin!</strong> 🎉</p>",
